&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction &lt;a href="#introduction" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>If you have a GoPro camera or another device that records MP4 videos and for some unexpected reason your video is corrupted for various reasons, it&amp;rsquo;s possible to recover the video without sound! It&amp;rsquo;s not ideal, but it&amp;rsquo;s better than losing everything.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Video Conversions</title><link>https://wiki.deimos.fr/Conversions_videos/</link><pubDate>Sun, 02 May 2010 21:43:00 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://wiki.deimos.fr/Conversions_videos/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction &lt;a href="#introduction" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>mencoder is one of the most used applications along with ffmpeg to convert or encode videos.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="installation">Installation &lt;a href="#installation" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Depending on what you will use, select only the one you wish:&lt;/p>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="d4e35db" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>apt-get install mencoder ffmpeg&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;p>If you want to create OGV (OGG/Theora) videos for HTML5, you need to install this package:&lt;/p>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="58cf76e" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>aptitude install ffmpeg2theora&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;h2 id="usage">Usage &lt;a href="#usage" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="convert-a-wmv-to-a-avi">Convert a .wmv to a .avi &lt;a href="#convert-a-wmv-to-a-avi" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>


 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="9a06af7" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>mencoder &amp;#34;/path/to/file.wmv&amp;#34; -ofps 23.976 -ovc lavc -oac copy -o &amp;#34;/path/to/file.avi&amp;#34;&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;h3 id="convert-a-mp4-to-a-avi">Convert a .mp4 to a .avi &lt;a href="#convert-a-mp4-to-a-avi" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>


 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="d96aaa1" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>ffmpeg -i &amp;#34;/path/to/file.mp4&amp;#34; &amp;#34;/path/to/file.avi&amp;#34;&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
